{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't bomb us really, but if a plane was hit, they used to jettison the bombs in order to make it lighter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they could make it back to-- to England, so they jettisoned, where-- wherever they could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they used to fall on our village, or the next village, or in-- or Grossenbrode in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And luckily, like I said, the houses were sort of spaced out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't-- it wasn't a heavily built area, so a lot of the bombs used to fall into open fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some, of course, also fell on houses, and it came to that kind of situation where almost every night, we were up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the beginning, I used to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to hear it in my sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- the bombing was so heavy, I used to hear it in my sleep.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything used to shake, but I used to sleep though.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, my mom-- my sister used to wake me up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was afraid and used to wake me up, and we used to sit downstairs and-- and-- to wait for whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's when I used to start going out and see what was happening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But to go back to the school part, they started-- the law came that we had to-- no longer could go to school after a certain date.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I remember the last day in school, you know, I remember the teacher being very unhappy about it, the Dutch teacher.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he said, I'm sorry that you have to go-- leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You always were good students, and-- and I hope you-- everything is going to be OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
